A really basic rails template, for the current (as of this writing) rails, 2.3.x

Uses: authlogic, cancan, shoulda, factory_girl, jrails, fast_context

Basic controllers for UserSessions, Users, and PasswordResets are built in. Some shoulda macros and a login_as method for testing with authlogic are also included.

Usage:

rails mynewapp -m path/to/basic_app/basic_app.rb